message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "AptadynamiK — PRAMA Protokol: ProbLog Monitor"
abstract: >-
  Structural viability monitoring for LLM generation trajectories using
  logprob-derived dynamics. Maps token-level uncertainty signals into a
  dynamic core with memory (tension, permissivity, contracting viability
  threshold, regime classification) to assess risk at the trajectory level.
